    "Establishing legal and reliable data exchange centers, anonymizing personal data, and standardizing data resource management are critical challenges.",
    "However, with the continuous advancement of AI methods and comprehensive hardware support, numerous cutting-edge approaches are emerging.",
    "These include using generative AI, quantum chemistry, and large models.",
    "In the future, quantum chemistry methods can leverage particlelevel information to handle molecular interaction data, optimize molecular structure design, and predict molecular reactions.",
    "Generative AI can learn from extensive data inputs to predict complex structures like protein folding, similar to AlphaFold, generating new compounds disruptively."
